craterdog.collections

Class Set<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • craterdog.collections.abstractions.Collection<E>
      • craterdog.collections.abstractions.OrderedCollection<E>
        • craterdog.collections.Set<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of element managed by the collection.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Accessible<E>, Iteratable<E>, Ordered<E>, Composite, Sequential<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>

    public class Set<E>
extends OrderedCollection<E>
    This collection class implements an ordered collection that does not allow duplicate elements. The implementation dynamically scales up and down the size of the underlying data structures as the number elements changes over time.
    Author:
    Derk Norton
